{"tid":2056864,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"［感謝］駐歐洲藝術組織辦網上節目「寧鳴而死，不默而生」　盼守港人歷史","createTime":"2020-06-09T04:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-09T04:03:04.000Z","uid":48083,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"8f95e5ee164bf2f265c7a1ba9d12c3dfba8c30c2","tid":2056864,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:02:06.000Z","msg":"抗爭持續一年，港人疲累卻未放棄，各自努力。抗爭行動從街頭到網絡世界，無處不在。駐歐洲藝術組織「Young Blood Initiative (YBI)」近日發起抗爭週年紀念計畫「Silence is Compliance：寧鳴而死，不默而生 」 ，6 月 12 日起在網上平台展出抗爭藝術作品、學術論文與小誌（Zine）內容等。<br />\n<br />\n「我一直想為至去年六月起的社會運動籌劃一週年紀念的計畫，只是我沒有足夠動力實現它。但自從『國安法』即將在香港落實，所有事情都改變了。」YBI 創辦人 Candy Choi 說。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H5zk73o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH5zk73o.jpg&h=14d8ac8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FfGr3BP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFfGr3BP.jpg&h=86e0592d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oEV4QgQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoEV4QgQ.jpg&h=93f8988e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HWjEac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HWjEac.jpg&h=eb5c9b0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Silence is Compliance: 寧鳴而死，不默而生」<br />\n<br />\n上線日期: 2020 年 6 月 12 日<br />\n<br />\n直播時間: 香港時間 6月12日 21:00 | 6月13日 02:00<br />\n<br />\n網站連結：<a href=\"http://www.silenceiscompliance.art\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.silenceiscompliance.art&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19vhh9XvCW3eHRhDz%2B7Q%2FvTo%3D&h=788469bb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.silenceiscompliance.art</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/culture/%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E4%B8%80%E5%B9%B4-%E9%A7%90%E6%AD%90%E6%B4%B2%E8%97%9D%E8%A1%93%E7%B5%84%E7%B9%94%E8%BE%A6%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE-%E5%AF%A7%E9%B3%B4%E8%80%8C%E6%AD%BB-%E4%B8%8D%E9%BB%98%E8%80%8C%E7%94%9F-%E7%9B